name: Sierra Madre Sunrise
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (1 oz)	Mezcal
  - (3/4 oz)	Aperol
  - (1/2 oz)	Lemon juice
  - (3 dashes)	Chocolate Bitters
  - (3 oz)	Club Soda
  - (1 peel)	Lemon


steps:
  - Fill shaker with ice
  - Add Mezcal, Aperol, lemon juice, and bitters
  - Shake well, until chilled
  - Fill rocks glass with fresh ice
  - Add club soda to glass
  - Strain cocktail on top
  - Garnish with lemon peel
